<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>139</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tho ingka ting ka Pa kawmah chieh ding ka ie,
 Ka ma meipi bangin a zing;
 Ei hehpih dang ka mu zo puoi, khawvel ahin,
 Ka pa lo chu ka dogal maw.

[V2]
 Gilo in taimang mah leng,
 A phatna tuoi ngeilo;
 Kisik a ka hawl kit chun,
 A zal zo kit ingka.

[V3]
 2. Ka Pa In a khan chu sum-le-pai a tamin,
 Mi lungkham cheng a hehnep sak;
 Kei sangawn mai leh gilkiel a thiding ka him?
 Banga gimthei guola ka vak?

[V4]
 3. Aw, a kawma ka chen lai kha a nuom na e,
 Khawvel hawihna ka hawl cheng cheng;
 Ka vak gel leh ka pa In sung ka ngai diek hi,
 Thupha chawi ding hilo ka him?

[V5]
 4. Kei gilo a hih lungkham leh zahhuoi sakpa,
 Kei dinga mun a phal chun aw!
 Zie khawvel pak ka dogal hi ngai ta puo'ng ka,
 A lun lai mawng a chawm taluoi.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Pa Kawm Zuonka</title>
</song>